### Fetch all tasks
GET http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new task
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "title": "test title",
    "date": "2022-11-09T12:00:00Z",
    "description": "This is a test description",
    "priority": "normal",
    "status": "todo"
}

### Update a task
PUT http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "id": "6bff8291-00fc-48da-8426-1bf16c2974c5",
    "status": "inProgress"
}